source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JHWlGy_JhJI
   git: https://github.com/iralabdisco/ira_laser_tools

1.add two new tf base on base_link
2.set two lidar base on the two new tf
	
3.add pkg(ira_laser_tools)
4.change your param
	set your tf link
       <param name="destination_frame" value="base_link" />	
       <param name="cloud_destination_topic" value="/merged_cloud" />
	set your topic name of merge two scan 
       <param name="scan_destination_topic"  value="/scan_multi" />
	set two scan topic which you want to merge
       <param name="laserscan_topics" value="/scan2 /scan" />
